headline: 2 Reasons to Like HUM and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Humana has gotten torched over the last six months - since November 2024, its stock price has dropped 24.3% to a new 52-week low of $224.50 per share. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
